item.title: [HIVE-22521] Both Driver and SessionState has a userName
item.description: This caused some confusing behaviour to me...especially when the 2 values were different.
item.summary: Both Driver and SessionState has a userName

status.description: The issue is considered finished, the resolution is correct. Issues which are not closed can be reopened.

comments.comment: I think at any time we should have only 1 userName thing...I think we should rely on SessionState and retire the one at the Driver level - or at least short-circuit it back to the SessionState based value
